SUMMARY:Houston TCG Con IX
DESCRIPTION:Houston TCG Con IX — Your Favorite TCG Weekend in Texas \nThree days. 100+ vendors. Every game that matters. Houston TCG Con IX is back — and the Texas TCG community keeps showing up stronger every round! \nPokémon. Yu-Gi-Oh!. Magic: The Gathering. One Piece. Lorcana. Riftbound. Dragon Ball Super. Digimon. Flesh and Blood. If it’s cardboard worth chasing\, it’s on this floor. \n  \n📅 Date: Friday–Sunday\, July 3–5\, 2026 \n⏰ Time: Friday: 3PM – 10PM | Saturday: 10AM – 6PM | Sunday: 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥 \n🃏 100+ TCG Vendors — Three Days of Cardboard Shop from 100+ vendors traveling from across Texas and beyond. Find singles\, sealed product\, booster boxes\, graded slabs\, Japanese imports\, and rare inserts across every major title — Pokémon\, MTG\, Yu-Gi-Oh!\, One Piece\, Lorcana\, Riftbound\, Dragon Ball Super\, Digimon\, Flesh and Blood\, and more. Come with a wantlist. Leave with something you weren’t expecting. \n  \n🤝 The Trade Floor Is Open Bring your binders\, your bulk\, your trade bait\, and your spec pulls. Houston TCG Con is a trade-friendly floor — deals happen naturally here because the people at the tables are collectors first. Three days means three days of opportunities to find the trade that makes your collection. \n  \n💸 Deals Across Every Budget From budget bulk and bargain boxes to high-end slabs and competitive singles — the floor has range. Whether you’re spec buying\, PC hunting\, or just looking to flip smart\, TCG Con IX has the inventory to make it happen. \n  \n💼 Vendor Space Available Table space is open for TCG and collectibles vendors. Come connect with the Texas TCG community. 👉 Apply here: https://forms.gle/KFdA1u3pKRAvNtzJ9 \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock In Your Rate We’ve secured a special hotel rate exclusively for TCG Con IX attendees. Book your stay and make it a full weekend. 👉 Book here \n  \nThree days. One floor. The best TCG weekend in Texas. Houston TCG Con IX — July 3–5.
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-tcg-con-ix/
CATEGORIES:Trading Card Game
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/HTX-Banner-IG-Reel-TCG-Con-IX.png
END:VEVENT
