SUMMARY:Artist Alley Houston III
DESCRIPTION:Artist Alley Houston III — 100+ Local Creators. All Original. All Handmade.\nPrint hunters\, charm collectors\, plushie lovers\, and fandom art fanatics — Artist Alley Houston III is your weekend. Two days\, 100+ local and regional creators\, and zero mass-produced merch. Every piece on every table was made by the person standing behind it. \n  \n📅 Date: Saturday–Sunday\, July 11–12\, 2026 \n⏰ Time: Saturday: 10AM – 6PM | Sunday: 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥 \n🎨 100+ Artists and Makers — All Fandoms\, All Styles Explore a curated marketplace packed with anime fan art\, original illustrations\, stickers\, enamel pins\, art prints\, zines\, plushies\, handcrafted charms\, crochet creations\, accessories\, fantasy artwork\, and pop-culture-inspired pieces — all original\, all handmade\, no AI-generated art. Whether you’re shopping for your wall\, your ita bag\, your shelf\, or just yourself\, this floor delivers. Come ready to discover your next favorite Houston creator. \n  \n✨ Exclusive Drops and Event Debuts Many artists are launching event-only merch\, limited bundles\, brand-new releases\, and first-time debuts created specifically for Artist Alley Houston III. You won’t find these anywhere else — online or in stores. Bring a tote bag. You’re going to need it. \n  \n💬 Meet the Makers Talk with the artists. Hear the stories behind the work. Commission something made just for you. This is not just a shopping floor — it’s where Houston’s creative community shows up in person. Fellow creators\, longtime collectors\, and first-time visitors all belong here. \n  \n🎁 FREE Artist Raffle Win original art\, stickers\, keychains\, and handmade goods donated by our featured artists. No purchase necessary — just stop by\, sign up\, and you’re in. Every ticket is a chance to go home with something one-of-a-kind. \n  \n💌 Join the Artist Lineup Table space is open for local artists and makers. Come build with the Houston creative community. 👉 Apply here \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock In Your Rate We’ve secured a special hotel rate exclusively for Artist Alley Houston III attendees. Book your stay and make it a full weekend. 👉 Book here \n  \nTwo days. 100+ creators. Art made with love\, sold in person. Artist Alley Houston III — July 11 & 12.
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/artist-alley-houston-iii/
CATEGORIES:Anime
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Banner.png
