SUMMARY:CCS Nerd Yard Sale III
DESCRIPTION:CCS Houston Nerd Yard Sale III — Dig In. Deal Out. Pass It On.\nGot shelves full of stuff that deserves a new home? Looking to score fan-loved finds at yard-sale prices? CCS Houston Nerd Yard Sale III is back for a full weekend — two days of clearing\, digging\, dealing\, and connecting with fellow fans across every fandom and era. \nThis isn’t a convention. It’s not a vendor hall. It’s a true community yard sale where real collectors clear their collections\, real deals get made\, and real conversations happen over shared fandoms. \n  \n📅 Date: Saturday–Sunday\, July 18–19\, 2026 \n⏰ Time: Saturday: 10AM – 6PM | Sunday: 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥 \n🧺 For Sellers — Clear Your Shelves\, Make Some Cash Got boxes of fandom stuff ready to move? Duplicates\, impulse buys\, collections you’ve outgrown? Set up a table\, meet fellow fans\, and pass your collection on to someone who’ll love it just as much as you did. Perfect for collectors downsizing\, families clearing closets\, and anyone who needs to make space. 👉 Apply to be a seller \n  \n🔍 For Shoppers — Dig\, Deal\, Discover Bargain hunters\, this floor is yours. Browse tables packed with fan-loved finds at yard-sale prices across every fandom and era. You never know what you’ll find — but here’s what might be waiting: \n\n📚 Comics\, manga\, and books\n🎮 Retro games and consoles — NES\, SNES\, Sega\, PlayStation classics\, and more\n🧸 Plushies\, pins\, keychains\, and gacha\n🧩 Anime merch\, figures\, and Funkos\n📼 VHS\, vintage media\, and old-school collectibles\n👕 Fandom fashion and accessories\n🃏 Cards\, toys\, and unexpected gems\n\nPrices are yard-sale friendly. Every table is different. The best finds are the ones you didn’t know you were looking for. \n  \n👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 All Fandoms. All Ages. Zero Gatekeeping. Bring the whole crew. No pressure. No gatekeeping. Just fans connecting with fans over the things they love. \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock In Your Rate We’ve secured a special hotel rate exclusively for Nerd Yard Sale III attendees. Book your stay and make it a full weekend. 👉 Book here \n  \nBring your trade boxes. Bring your shopping bags. Bring your inner treasure hunter. CCS Houston Nerd Yard Sale III — July 18 & 19.
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/ccs-nerd-yard-sale-iii/
CATEGORIES:Action Figure & Toy,Anime,Comic,Video Game
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Banner-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
