SUMMARY:Houston World of Hot Wheels IV
DESCRIPTION:🚗🏁 Houston World of Hot Wheels IV is roaring back with more thrills and speed! 🏁🚗\nAfter an electric\, action-packed weekend of nonstop deals\, racing\, and collector excitement\, Houston World of Hot Wheels IV is revving up for another round! We’re bringing even MORE vendors\, MORE cars\, and MORE action for collectors\, racers\, and families to enjoy all weekend long. ⚡ \n  \n📅 July 25–26\, 2026 | 10AM–5PM\n📍 9700 Bissonnet St 1500\, Houston\, TX\n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \nEvent Highlights\n🛒 Hot Wheels Swap & Shop – Both Days \n50+ vendors. 30\,000+ Hot Wheels\, Matchbox\, and diecast to dig through. STHs\, TH variations\, premium Car Culture\, redline-era pieces\, MOC vintage\, loose mainline bins\, M2s\, Greenlights\, Johnny Lightnings. Bring your want list! \n  \n🚗✨ Houston Diecast Custom Contest – 10AM-3PM | Both Days \nCalling all builders and custom kings 👑 Bring your best custom Hot Wheels/Matchbox build — paint\, wheel swaps\, stance\, body kits\, full one-of-one creations. This contest is for the detail freaks and the true “trust the process” customizers. 🏆 The winner will be announced at 4PM and will receive a prize sponsored by Domingo! ✨ Hosted by @funopolistoys \n  \n🏁 Hot Wheels Racing Contest – Both Days\nThe stage track is live all weekend. Hourly races\, prizes for winners\, FREE to enter. \n  \n🏎️ Car Show (Parking Lot Showcase) \nTake it outside and check out Houston’s coolest real-life rides. Style\, horsepower\, and car-community energy all in one spot. \n  \n👶 Mini Zones & Family Fun\nFun spaces for younger collectors and first‑time racers — all ages welcome! \n  \n🚨 VENDORS WANTED\nGot STHs\, vintage redlines\, custom builds\, or bulk mainline to move? This is your crowd.\n📥 Apply: https://tinyurl.com/CCSGuestVendorFromHouston \n  \n🏨 Special Hotel Deals\nEnjoy a special room rate of $79/night at TownePlace Suites\, just about 15 minutes from the venue!\n👉 Book: https://www.marriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-link.mi?id=1767823967549&key=CORP&app=resvlink \n  \nHunt or race. Trade or just walk the floor. The customs will be parked outside\, the bins will be open inside\, and the track will be running all weekend. See you July 25–26.
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-world-of-hot-wheels-iv/
CATEGORIES:Action Figure & Toy
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Event-Launch-Kit-Houston-World-of-Hot-Wheels-IV.png
END:VEVENT
