SUMMARY:Back to School Yugioh Tournament
DESCRIPTION:Join us on July 31 for a special Back-to-School Yu-Gi-Oh Tournament Hosted by Eclectic Nerdz. where your entry helps local students get ready for the new school year. Instead of an entry fee\, bring $10+ worth of new\, sealed school supplies and compete for prizes while supporting a great cause. \n  \nPlay\, give back\, and help make a difference—one duel at a time! \n🗓️ : July 31\, 2026 \n📍: 9700 Bissonnet St\, #1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n  \nEvent Overview: \n\nFormat: Advanced\nTournament Structure: Swiss Rounds\nExpected Number of Rounds: 5\, Rounds based on Attendance\nEntry: Sealed School supplies of $10 value or more\nOn-Site Registration\n\n  \n💰 Prize Pool: \n\n1st Place: Booster Box Chaos Origins and Yugioh Playmat\n2nd Place: 12 packs of Chaos Origins and Yugioh Playmat\n3rd Place: 6 Packs of Chaos Origins Yugioh Playmat\n\n  \n📋 Registration Details: \n\nRegistration begins at 6 PM\nRound 1 Starts at 6:45 PM
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/back-to-school-yugioh-tournament/
CATEGORIES:Trading Card Game
