SUMMARY:CCS $20\,000 cEDH Invitational Qualifier #3
DESCRIPTION:🏆 CCS $20\,000 cEDH Invitational Qualifier #3 🏆\nThe race tightens. The margins shrink. \nQualifier #3 brings us into the mid season of the CCS $50\,000 cEDH Invitational Series. With only three events after\, every decision matters and every point is gold. \nFull Details → https://topdeck.gg/event/ccs-50000-cedh-invitational \n  \n🗓 Dates: August 1–2\, 2026 \n📍 Location: Charlie’s Collectible Show\, 9700 Bissonett St Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n\nTournament Details:\n\n🎟️ Entry Fee: $90 before July 18\, $110 After\n🔗 Register Now! 👉  https://topdeck.gg/event/css-20000-cedh-invitational-qualifier-4\n\n🗂️ Format & Structure\n\nFormat: cEDH (Proxy Friendly)\nSaturday: 6 Swiss Rounds (based on attendance)\nSunday: 2 Swiss Rounds → Top 16\n\n🚫 Proxy Requirements: \n\nFull card name\, mana cost\, type line\, and effect text\nTest cards or clearly written MDFCs allowed\nNo paper slip-ins permitted\n\n💰 Guaranteed $20\,000 Prize Pool\n\n1st — $5\,000 + Auto Invite + TopDeck Invite + 200 pts\n2nd-4th — $2\,000 each + Auto Invite + 160 pts\n5th–8th — $550 + 120 pts\n9th–16th — $550 + 100 pts\n17th–32nd — $175 + 75 pts\n33rd–48th — 60 pts\n49th–64th — 45 pts\n65th–96th — 30 pts\n97th–128th — 20 pts\n\nEvent Schedule:\n🕔 Registration Opens: 9 AM \n🕔 Player Meeting (Day 1): 10 AM \n🕔 Day 2 Start Time: 9 AM \n🛍️ Collectible Marketplace\nBetween rounds\, enjoy access to a curated marketplace featuring: \n\nTCG singles\, sealed\, and accessories\nRetro video games & consoles\nAnime merch\, figures\, and models\nToys and other hobby collectibles\n\nPerfect for grabbing upgrades\, browsing grails\, or just hanging out between matches. \n🏨 Special Hotel Deals\nEnjoy a special rate of $79/night — 2 Queens at TownePlace Suites\, only 15 minutes distance from the action! \nBook your stay 👉🏻 https://www.marriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-link.mi?id=1767823967549&key=CORP&app=resvlink \n🔔 IMPORTANT REMINDERS\n\nPlayer names will appear as real names on published documents.\nTop 16 decklists will be published.\n\n🔥 Late-season stakes hit hard — tighten your game and push forward. Your run to the $50K Invitational continues at CCS cEDH Qualifier #3!
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/ccs-20000-cedh-invitational-qualifier-3/
CATEGORIES:Trading Card Game
