SUMMARY:Houston Comic Exchange II
DESCRIPTION:Houston Comic Exchange II – Built for Comic Collectors\nSummer is prime comic-hunting season\, and CCS Houston Comic Exchange II brings together collectors\, dealers\, and fans for a day of buying\, selling\, trading\, and discovering comics. From key issues and first appearances to hidden gems and box-fresh finds\, every table offers something worth digging for. \nNo gatekeeping\, no pressure\, just comics and the people who love them. \n  \n📅 Saturday\, August 1\, 2026 | 10AM – 5PM \n📍 9700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥\n📦 50 Vendor Tables – All Comics\, All Formats \nSingles\, back issues\, key issues\, first appearances\, graded slabs\, raw runs\, indie and small press\, variant covers. Vendor tables dedicated entirely to comics\, no toys\, no filler. If you’re a comic collector\, this floor was built for you. \n  \n🔍 Key Issues and First Appearances \nThis is where the hunt lives. Vendors bring the deep cuts\, raw back issues worth digging through\, graded books if you’re chasing condition\, and the kind of keys that actually show up when serious collectors are clearing their own collections to make room. \n  \n📚 Back-Issue Digging and Indie Discovery \nNot every great find is a grail. Long boxes of back issues across decades and publishers\, plus indie comics and small press titles that never make it to a standard shop shelf. Come with a list or come ready to browse – both work. \n  \n🤝 Vendors Who Collect Too \nThe people behind these tables are the same people who will ask what you’re hunting before they start pulling books for you. The Houston Comic Exchange is a community floor first. The conversations are part of the event. \n  \n🛒 Vendor Table Applications \nHouston comic vendors: we’re gathering a focused comics-only crowd\, and free entry is driving serious foot traffic. Apply for your table here 👉🏻 https://forms.gle/7q6pjcoiJTPbJouP8 \n  \nThe key issue you’ve been tracking is probably in one of those long boxes this summer. The Houston Comic Exchange II\, August 1. Free entry\, free parking\, always.
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-comic-exchange-ii/
CATEGORIES:Comic
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Banner.jpg
END:VEVENT
