SUMMARY:Houston Toy Exchange III
DESCRIPTION:Houston Toy Exchange III — The Floor Is Loaded\, Houston\nSomewhere on this floor is the piece you have been hunting for months. 🔥 \nHouston Toy Exchange III is a pure toy marketplace\, no convention noise\, no filler. Just collectors\, families\, and dealers moving action figures\, vintage finds\, and modern grails across one packed floor at CCS Houston. The fun is in the hunt: digging through a bin you have never seen\, talking shop with someone who knows the line better than you do\, and walking out with something you did not expect to find. \n  \n📅 Date: Sunday\, August 2\, 2026 | 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St\, #1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 What You’ll Find on the Floor 🔥 \n🛍️ Toy Marketplace Tables packed with action figures\, vintage toys\, sealed and loose\, nostalgia pieces\, and the modern lines collectors are actually chasing right now. Every table is its own dig. Come search the floor. \n  \n💰 Buy\, Sell\, Trade Bring the toys you are ready to pass along or trade up for something you have been chasing. Collectors and vendors are buying\, selling\, and trading all day. Connect\, negotiate\, and keep great pieces moving through the community. \n  \n🔍 Toy Appraisals Holding something and not sure what it’s worth? One of our experienced vendors is running toy appraisals all day\, sharing insights on value\, rarity\, and trade potential so you can make confident\, informed deals on the floor. \n  \n🧩 Toy Scavenger Hunt Challenge Turn the hunt into a game. Work the marketplace and complete the Toy Hunt Challenge by tracking down specific toy categories across multiple booths for a shot at prizes and collector bragging rights. \n  \n📸 Toy Flex Wall Score something special? Show it off. Snap a photo of your best pickup at the Toy Flex Wall and share your find with the community. \n  \nLongtime collector or just starting out\, Houston Toy Exchange III is about connecting\, swapping stories\, and keeping the love of toys alive together. Bring your toys\, bring your curiosity\, pull up. \n  \nWant in as a vendor? Tables are open: https://tinyurl.com/CCSGuestVendorFromHouston \n  \nHouston Toy Exchange III. Bring your toys\, bring your curiosity\, and come move some pieces.
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-toy-exchange-iii/
CATEGORIES:Action Figure & Toy
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Event-Launch-Kit-Houston-Toy-Exchange-III.png
