SUMMARY:Houston TCG Con X
DESCRIPTION:🃏 Houston TCG Con X | Every Format. One Floor. Three Days. 🃏\nThree days. Every format in the room. The Houston TCG community takes over CCS August 7–9 for Pokémon\, MTG\, One Piece\, Lorcana\, and Yu-Gi-Oh. Tournament grinders and binder flippers on the same floor\, doing what this community does best. \n  \n📅 Date: Friday–Sunday\, August 7–9\, 2026 \n⏰ Time: Friday: 3PM–10PM | Saturday: 10AM–6PM | Sunday: 10AM–5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥 \n🃔 Multi-Game Vendor Floor \nPokémon. MTG. One Piece. Lorcana. Yu-Gi-Oh. Singles vendors\, sealed product\, and binder traders across every major format. Three full days to hunt\, flip\, and deal face-to-face. \n  \n🏆 Multi-Game Tournaments \nCompetitive rounds running all weekend across formats. Tournament schedule and registration details coming soon. Follow CCS Houston for updates. \n  \n📦 Full Marketplace \nSports cards\, anime merch\, figures\, comics\, and toys rounding out the vendor floor for everything you collect beyond the card game. \n  \n💼 Vendor Tables Available \nTCG dealers\, singles vendors\, sports card sellers\, anime and collectible booths. Houston’s biggest TCG weekend is yours. Apply: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdei0apYj2qU4fQIiz9rrqVDHgqmFZSpLRzYDAufcg3B8BaXA/viewform \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock Your Room \nGroup rate available at Marriott. Book before it fills: https://www.marriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-link.mi?id=1767823967549&key=CORP&app=resvlink \nThree days\, every format\, free entry. See you in August\, Houston.
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-tcg-con-x/
CATEGORIES:Trading Card Game
