UID:75826-1786788000-1786899600@ccs-houston.com
SUMMARY:Retro Video Game Expo III
DESCRIPTION:🕹️ Houston\, Press Start on a Weekend of Pure Retro Nostalgia! 👾 \nStep back into the golden era of gaming at Retro Video Game Expo III\, a two-day celebration of classic consoles\, arcade legends\, competitive retro tournaments\, and nonstop free play. From expanded free-play zones spanning the 80s and beyond to live\, high-energy tournament matchups and a collector-focused marketplace\, this expo is built for gamers who chase high scores and grail finds. \n  \n🗓️ Date & Time: August 15–16\, 2026 | 10AM–5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St #1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n💥 FREE ENTRY. FREE PARKING. FREE PLAY. \n\n🎮 Event Highlights\n🎮 Retro Video Game Marketplace – All Weekend \nStep into a collector’s paradise. Vendors from across the region are bringing vintage consoles\, original cartridges\, imports\, manuals\, accessories\, and hard-to-find titles. This is where treasures respawn. \n🚨 Want to vend? Sign up here 👉 https://tinyurl.com/HoustonVendors \n  \n🎮 Free-Play Zone – ALL Day \nJump on 80’s Arcades & Classic Consoles and relive the games that made gaming legendary. More setups and activities to be announced soon! \n\n🤝 Calling All Collaborators & Retro Communities\nThis event is built with the community for community! We’re actively looking to partner with: \n🏁 Tournament organizers → https://forms.gle/74Qvuv9PFzeDVF1V8 \n🕹️ Pinball/Arcade Hosts → https://forms.gle/74Qvuv9PFzeDVF1V8 \n🎤 Workshops & Panels → https://forms.gle/q2nCKsZ6FEVZBgqW9 \n🙌 Volunteer Sign-Up → https://forms.gle/15zMGTqZPSGKjGdy6 \n🎮 Vendor Applications → https://tinyurl.com/CCSGuestVendorFromHouston \nIf you’ve ever wanted to be part of event\, bring your passion! Let’s chat! 📩 \n  \n🏨 Special Hotel Deals \nEnjoy a special rate of $79/night — 2 Queens at TownePlace Suites\, only 15 minutes distance from the action! \nBook your stay 👉🏻 https://www.marriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-link.mi?id=1767823967549&key=CORP&app=resvlink \n  \nBring your crew\, grab a controller\, and let’s relive the golden age of gaming together. 👾✨
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/retro-video-game-expo-iii/
CATEGORIES:Video Game
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Banner-5.png
END:VEVENT
