UID:91970-1787997600-1788109200@ccs-houston.com
SUMMARY:CCS Card Show I
DESCRIPTION:CCS Card Show I — Every Sport. Every TCG. One Floor.\nHouston\, the hobby comes home. For the first time at CCS\, every major sport and every major TCG land under one roof: sports card collectors\, memorabilia hunters\, and TCG players moving cards on the same floor\, the way it should be. Modern hits to vintage grails\, sealed wax to graded slabs\, raw singles to game-used pieces. Buy\, sell\, trade\, grade. This is the room. \n  \n📅 Date: August 29-30\, 2026 | 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥 \n⚾ The Ultimate Sports Card & Memorabilia Marketplace \nExplore vendors dedicated to sports cards\, high-end memorabilia\, and rare collectibles from baseball\, football\, basketball\, and more. If you’re hunting for a signed rookie card\, vintage set\, or exclusive autograph\, this is THE place to level up your collection. \n  \n🃏 Trading Card Game Extravaganza 🃏 \nWe’re also featuring top TCG vendors offering a treasure trove of Pokémon\, Yu-Gi-Oh!\, Magic: The Gathering\, One Piece\, Lorcana\, and more! Chase that elusive rare pull or build your deck for your next tournament\, you’ll find the best deals on booster packs\, graded singles\, sealed products\, and Japanese imports. \n  \n💼 Vendors Wanted \nGot a table’s worth to move? Guest vendors are welcome at Card Show I. The person across the table is a fan like you. Claim your spot 👉🏻 https://forms.gle/sZdrRxHkEXM69kbN6 \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock In Your Rate\nEnjoy a special rate of $79/night — ****2 Queens at TownePlace Suites\, only 15 minutes away from the action! 👉 https://www.marriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-link.mi?id=1767823967549&key=CORP&app=resvlink \n  \nHouston’s first CCS Card Show. Every sport\, every TCG\, one floor. Pull up.
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/ccs-card-show-i/
CATEGORIES:Sports Card,Trading Card Game
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Event-Launch-Kit-CCS-Card-Show-I-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
