UID:77376-1789812000-1789837200@ccs-houston.com
SUMMARY:Demon Slayer Mini Con
DESCRIPTION:🔥 Calling all Demon Slayer Corps members\, Hashira-in-training\, and Tanjiro fans**!** 🔥\nFrom Mizunoto beginners to seasoned Hashira\, masters of Sun Breathing to the loyal members of the Zenitsu-squad\, Demon Slayer Mini Con is your next mission! CCS Houston is hosting a one-day Total Concentration event for every slayer who lives for the Hinokami Kagura\, the intensity of the Upper Rank battles\, and the bond between friends. \nJoin the Corps for a day packed with Nichirin-grade marketplace finds\, Cosplay haoris\, and Blood Demon Art energy\, all in a fan-first space where no one is left in the Final Selection alone. \nSteel your heart\, grab your Kasugai Crow\, and let’s set our hearts ablaze together ⚔️✨ \n  \n🗓️ Date & Time: Saturday\, Sept 19\, 2026 | 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St\, #1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n👘 Demon Slayer Cosplay Showcase + Demon Face-Off (2 PM)\nPrepare for a Hashira-level showdown in a dramatic pose-off against our “demon.” The crowd’s roar will determine who survives the night and claims victory. \n  \n🎴 Nichirin Sword Pose-Off (3PM)\nEven without a uniform\, your spirit can burn bright! Grab a Nichirin blade\, take the stage\, and unleash your most iconic Breathing Style pose for a chance to win a prize. \n  \n🎮 Demon Slayer: Hinokami Chronicles Free-Play Zone (All Day)\nJump into the action in our gaming area! Join free play sessions on the Demon Slayer: The Hinokami Chronicles video game and challenge fellow slayers to a dueling trial. \n  \nDemon Slayer Trivia (3:30 PM)\nOnly those with the sharpest focus will survive this mental trial and earn their rank as a true scholar of the series. \n  \n🎨 Nezuko’s Box DIY Craft Station (All Day)\nChannel your inner Urokodaki to construct a miniature wooden-style carrier using paper\, charms\, and markers. Open to all ages! \n  \n🔥 Demon Slayer Artist Alley\nWander through a marketplace filled with hand-forged treasures and fandom collectibles\, including custom Nichirin charms\, Demon Slayer-inspired prints\, and talismans for the next mission\, our Artist Alley features the most talented creators in the Corps. \n🔥 Want to create something special for Demon Slayer fans? \n🔗 Host activities\, workshops\, or panels → https://forms.gle/q2nCKsZ6FEVZBgqW9 \n🔗 Volunteer Sign-Up → https://forms.gle/15zMGTqZPSGKjGdy6 \n🔗 Vendor Applications → https://tinyurl.com/HoustonVendors
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/demon-slayer-mini-con/
CATEGORIES:Anime
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/HOUSTON-Event-Launch-Kit-Demon-Slayer-Mini-Con.jpg
END:VEVENT
